openattic (1.0.7-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Add dependency to rrdtool.
  * Add openattic-module-cron package.
  * Add openattic user to nagios group.
  * Drop dependency to libpam-pgsql.
  * Drop dependency to zfs-fuse and ntfs-3g.
  * Add xfsprogs to recommends:.
  * Add openattic-module-twraid package.
  * Add openattic-module-ipmi package.
  * Install updatetwraid cron job.
  * Add a preinstall script that converts RRDs for STORAGE_TYPE=MULTIPLE.
  * Remove openattic-module-ftp-{my,pg}sql packages which have been replaced by
    a single openattic-module-ftp package.
  * Add dependency to proftpd-mod-winbind for oa-m-ftp.
  * Remove openattic-full-mysql and openattic-mysql packages.
  * Rename openattic-full-pgsql to openattic-full.
  * Add dependency to winbind, krb5-user, samba-common-bin and libnss-winbind
    for oa-m-samba.
  * Remove outdated oa-m-munin package.
  * Remove ajaxterm dependency.
  * Replace ifenslave dependency with ifenslave-2.6.
  * Add zfsonlinux to recommends:.
  * Depend on Django 1.4.
  * Add ocfs2-tools to suggests:.
  * Add vcs-hg: tag.
  * Remove dependency to python-matplotlib.
  * Add dependency to python-gobject.
  * Add sudo to recommends:.
  * Add dummy export to ensure nfs-kernel-server starts.

 -- Michael Ziegler <diese-addy@funzt-halt.net>  Wed, 08 May 2013 11:46:09 +0200

